CONTEXT DifferenceTypeCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT DifferenceTypeCheck
{+ Test that difference succeeds when both operands have the same signature.
   This verifies the type checker correctly accepts t[A*C] - r[A*C] yielding [A*C]. +}

RELATION r[A*C]
RELATION t[A*C]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testDifference: result = t - r

ENDCONTEXT
